directions: ["Combine pretzels,", "margarine", "and", "2 tablespoons sugar. Pat into bottom of a 13 x 9-inch pan.", "Bake 8 minutes at 400\u00b0. Combine Jell-O in water; add strawberries and stir well.", "Cool until soft set."]
